    "elements": [
        {
            "id": "t-1",
            "type": "text",
            "x": 200,
            "y": 200,
            "width": 1500,
            "height": 200,
            "text": "From Todo to Systems\nArchitecting Software in the LLM Era",
            "fontSize": 64,
            "fontFamily": "hand-drawn"
        },
        {
            "id": "t-2",
            "type": "text",
            "x": 200,
            "y": 450,
            "width": 1500,
            "height": 200,
            "text": "Code is no longer scarce.\nClarity is.",
            "fontSize": 36,
            "fontFamily": "hand-drawn"
        },
        {
            "id": "t-3",
            "type": "text",
            "x": 200,
            "y": 200,
            "width": 1500,
            "height": 300,
            "text": "Why this talk?\n\n• LLMs generate code\n• Engineers read & validate code\n• Architecture becomes the main skill",
            "fontSize": 36
        },
        {
            "id": "t-4",
            "type": "text",
            "x": 200,
            "y": 200,
            "width": 1500,
            "height": 300,
            "text": "Core Thesis\n\nEngineers are no longer typists.\nEngineers are Architects, Directors, Validators.",
            "fontSize": 42
        },
        {
            "id": "t-5",
            "type": "text",
            "x": 200,
            "y": 200,
            "width": 1500,
            "height": 300,
            "text": "Everything begins with a Todo.\n\nTwitter, CRM, ERP, SaaS are Todos with metadata.",
            "fontSize": 40
        },
        {
            "id": "t-6",
            "type": "text",
            "x": 200,
            "y": 200,
            "width": 1500,
            "height": 350,
            "text": "Todo teaches:\n• State transitions\n• UI as projection of data\n• Complexity grows predictably",
            "fontSize": 36
        },
        {
            "id": "t-7",
            "type": "text",
            "x": 200,
            "y": 200,
            "width": 1500,
            "height": 350,
            "text": "The Belt System\n\nWhite → CRUD\nYellow → Performance\nOrange → Auth\nGreen → Relationships",
            "fontSize": 38
        },
        {
            "id": "t-8",
            "type": "text",
            "x": 200,
            "y": 200,
            "width": 1500,
            "height": 350,
            "text": "Auth changes everything.\n\nData now has ownership.\nAuthorization becomes contextual.",
            "fontSize": 38
        },
        {
            "id": "t-9",
            "type": "text",
            "x": 200,
            "y": 200,
            "width": 1500,
            "height": 350,
            "text": "Relationships are the core.\n\nOne-to-one\nOne-to-many\nMany-to-many",
            "fontSize": 38
        },
        {
            "id": "t-10",
            "type": "text",
            "x": 200,
            "y": 200,
            "width": 1500,
            "height": 350,
            "text": "Frontend mindset:\nUI is a projection of metadata.",
            "fontSize": 38
        },
        {
            "id": "t-11",
            "type": "text",
            "x": 200,
            "y": 200,
            "width": 1500,
            "height": 350,
            "text": "Backend mindset:\nBehavior is a projection of metadata.",
            "fontSize": 38
        },
        {
            "id": "t-12",
            "type": "text",
            "x": 200,
            "y": 200,
            "width": 1500,
            "height": 400,
            "text": "Backend building blocks:\n• Domain model\n• Database\n• Rules\n• Messaging\n• Integrations\n• Instrumentation",
            "fontSize": 36
        },
        {
            "id": "t-13",
            "type": "text",
            "x": 200,
            "y": 200,
            "width": 1500,
            "height": 400,
            "text": "Rules are business logic.\n\nDynamic, versioned, explainable.",
            "fontSize": 38
        },
        {
            "id": "t-14",
            "type": "text",
            "x": 200,
            "y": 200,
            "width": 1500,
            "height": 400,
            "text": "Messaging enables scale.\n\nAsync workflows\nRetries\nReplays\nDLQ",
            "fontSize": 36
        },
        {
            "id": "t-15",
            "type": "text",
            "x": 200,
            "y": 200,
            "width": 1500,
            "height": 400,
            "text": "Instrumentation is the nervous system.\n\nEmit system events.\nEmit business events.",
            "fontSize": 36
        },
        {
            "id": "t-16",
            "type": "text",
            "x": 200,
            "y": 200,
            "width": 1500,
            "height": 400,
            "text": "LLMs write code.\n\nHumans define meaning.",
            "fontSize": 42
        },
        {
            "id": "t-17",
            "type": "text",
            "x": 200,
            "y": 200,
            "width": 1500,
            "height": 400,
            "text": "Engineer role shift:\n\nFrom coder → Architect → Director",
            "fontSize": 42
        },
        {
            "id": "t-18",
            "type": "text",
            "x": 200,
            "y": 200,
            "width": 1500,
            "height": 400,
            "text": "Feed LLMs:\n\n• Metadata\n• State machines\n• Rules\n• Events\n• Constraints",
            "fontSize": 36
        },
        {
            "id": "t-19",
            "type": "text",
            "x": 200,
            "y": 200,
            "width": 1500,
            "height": 400,
            "text": "Unified model:\n\nState + Behavior + Decisions + Events",
            "fontSize": 42
        },
        {
            "id": "t-20",
            "type": "text",
            "x": 200,
            "y": 200,
            "width": 1500,
            "height": 400,
            "text": "Final thought:\n\nCode is cheap.\nArchitecture is leverage.",
            "fontSize": 42
        }
    ],
